      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Risk-Based Classification of Accessories Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill revises how accessories to medical devices are classified. Specifically, the Food and Drug Administration must classify accessories based on the risks when used as intended<b>,</b> notwithstanding the classification of any other device with which such accessory is intended to be used. </p>]]></text>
